Documentation:
Install all the required dependency and node js also
-npm init -y
-npm install express body-parser typescript ts-node @types/node @types/express
after the run the command, create tsconfig.json file for configure the typescript
-create src folder inside create app.ts file and write code for api.
-run the code
-npm start
check the api
GET method call
http://localhost:8080/api/product
 
GET for protuct id :
http://localhost:8080/api/product/1
 
POST method write json data for post:
http://localhost:8080/api/product

 

PUT method call for update:
http://localhost:8080/api/product/12
 

DELETE method call for delete by id
http://localhost:8080/api/product/12
 




